    "text": [
        "Dear Mr. Aseem",
        "I am one of your students who is attending evenin classes for the french laguage. I am writing this letter to inform you that I am not able to continue my language course anymore.",
        "Having said that, though i would really wanted to continue, it is quite difficlut for me to manage a full time job and my family's responsibilities altogether. Since my husband has changed his job and he has to do a night shift, I left with no option as there would be no one to take care of my kid. Moreover it takes me two hours from my office to reach the classes.",
